  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t「蝶戀花」新譯<br/>\r\n我撇了棄婦你沒了老公，<br/>\r\n兩個死鬼勾肩搭背開房進了廣寒宮，<br/>\r\n笑問酒保有啥可助興，<br/>\r\n小二吳剛捧出桂花酒兩鍾。<br/>\r\n寂寞的嫦娥姐姐興冲冲，<br/>\r\n披上舞衣，<br/>\r\n擺腰扭臀獻藝外太空，<br/>\r\n忽然聽到俺位登九五，<br/>\r\n百感交集、涙如泉湧，頓足捶胸：<br/>\r\n千萬蕩婦淫娃，<br/>\r\n都便宜了那個殺千刀的冤家毛澤東！<br/>\n<br/>\r\n原詞<br/>\r\n我失驕陽君失栁<br/>\r\n楊柳輕颺直上重霄九<br/>\r\n問訊吳剛何所有<br/>\r\n吳剛捧出桂花酒<br/>\r\n寂寞嫦娥舒廣袖<br/>\r\n萬里長空且為忠魂舞<br/>\r\n忽報人間曾伏虎<br/>\r\n淚飛頓作傾盆雨<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOTk5M2ViMGZiZDQ1YjdmMWJlMWQ2LmpwZz93aWR0aD01MDAmaGVpZ2h0PTM3NQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9993eb0fbd45b7f1be1d6.jpg?width=500&amp;height=375\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9993eb0fbd45b7f1be1d6.jpg?width=500&amp;height=375\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9993eb0fbd45b7f1be1d6.jpg?width=500&amp;height=375\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
